    {
      "id": "p2-note",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 760,
      "width": 410,
      "height": 140,
      "text": "🧠 Why K2 and K4 don't move:\n• Their previous winner is still in the cluster.\n• Their weights for B and C never changed.\n• So argmax over {B, C} gives the same answer.\n\n👉 No avalanche. No mass cache miss.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
